"   Antihemophilic factor/von Willebrand factor complex (human): Patient drug information",
"  </div>",
"  <div id=\"lexiTitleImg\">",
"   <img height=\"17\" src=\"./../images/lexiComp/Lexicomp_2012_71x17.myextg\" width=\"71\"/>",
"  </div>",
